listing_description: Take a break from your busy city life & unwind at this beautiful beach retreat. Silvermoon is located right on Cox's Bazar Marine drive & just steps away from the pristine Inani beach. Enjoy the breathtaking view of the beautiful sea from your living room or terrace. Take a walk or hike in the mountains & lush forests which are less than a mile away. Restaurants & shops are a quick drive away. Relax with the whole family at this peaceful place to stay.
